snippet.title: Idol Showdown: Hoshimachi Suisei Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Character Debut Trailer: Hoshimachi Suisei / 星街すいせい ☄️

Suisei slashes her way into Idol Showdown!
すいせい、Idol Showdownに斬り込む！

Join the #IdolShowdown for FREE, coming Spring 2023.
